    Subinterfaces of CircuitModifier in squire.circuit
    Modifier and Type
    Interface
    Description
    interface 
    CombinableCircuitModifier
    The CombinableCircuitModifier interface extends CircuitModifier and represents a circuit modifier that can be combined with another CombinableCircuitModifier for circuit optimization.
    interface 
    UncombinableCircuitModifier
    The UncombinableCircuitModifier interface extends CircuitModifier and represents a circuit modifier that cannot be combined with other circuit modifiers for optimization.

    class 
    QuantumGate
    The QuantumGate class is an abstract implementation of the CombinableCircuitModifier interface, representing a quantum gate that can be applied to a quantum state vector.
